abstract: World Scrabble Championship in Warsaw, Poland, is momentarily halted when contestants notice missing letter tile, which had to be replaced by referee after search failed to turn it up.
snippet: Two competitors at the World Scrabble Championships in Warsaw were asked to empty their pockets when a “G” tile disappeared.
lead_paragraph: Two competitors at the World Scrabble Championships in Warsaw were asked to empty their pockets when a “G” tile disappeared.
